snippet.title: Pikmin 3: Special Holiday Hack Trailer (WIP)
snippet.description:
Big thanks to LazyBoii for lots of help with textures, and for just being super chill and awesome.

Credit goes to LazyBoii for all textures for the modified title screen, maps, walls, ramps and boxes.

Pikmin font found on fontmeme.com and made by: TheAdorableOshawott
